    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This stiff, cloth pouch is embroidered with whimsical images of playful pets. When you perform your daily preparations in the presence of your creature companion, three treats appear in the bag: an encouraging treat, a reward treat, and a soothing treat. These treats are always suitable for your companion and last until the next time you perform your daily preparations.",
