                        "type": "stat_block_section",
                        "subtype": "action_type",
                        "name": "One Action"
                    },
                    "effect": "You  *Command* your companion. Until the end of your turn, it gains a +5-foot status bonus to each of its Speeds, but must use at least one action to move closer to you.",
